<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='410000' id='t-410000'>And so this is part of what life is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413000' id='t-413000'>but it's not all of what life is.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='416000' id='t-416000'>And over the past few years,</span>
