<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='512000' id='t-512000'>The second insight</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='514000' id='t-514000'>is that emotions are at the center of our thinking.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='517000' id='t-517000'>People with strokes and lesions</span>
