<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='569000' id='t-569000'>So me talking about emotion</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='571000' id='t-571000'>is like Gandhi talking about gluttony,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='573000' id='t-573000'>but it is the central organizing process</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='575000' id='t-575000'>of the way we think.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='577000' id='t-577000'>It tells us what to imprint.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='579000' id='t-579000'>The brain is the record of the feelings of a life.</span>
