 9:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='581000' id='t-581000'>And the third insight</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='583000' id='t-583000'>is that we're not primarily self-contained individuals.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='587000' id='t-587000'>We're social animals, not rational animals.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590000' id='t-590000'>We emerge out of relationships,</span>
