<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='595000' id='t-595000'>And so when we see another person,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597000' id='t-597000'>we reenact in our own minds</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='599000' id='t-599000'>what we see in their minds.</span>
