<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='631000' id='t-631000'>We are now children of the French Enlightenment.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635000' id='t-635000'>We believe that reason is the highest of the faculties.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='638000' id='t-638000'>But I think this research shows</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='640000' id='t-640000'>that the British Enlightenment, or the Scottish Enlightenment,</span>
